heading: Demonâ€™s Wake Dungeon Guide
content: Demon's Wake is an annoying dungeon with a Slay all enemies objective combined with the Fallen monster family, which frequently revives small enemies. This makes completion a pain, so don't look to run this dungeon over and over again for XP. At least it offers Renown and the to make it worth your time once. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
